Benin Seeking to Sell Majority Stake in State Telecoms Company, ORTB Says

-- B y   S e r g e - D a v i d   Z o u e m e
-- 
2011-06-06T16:49:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/benin-seeking-to-sell-majority-stake-in-state-telecoms-company-ortb-says.html
Benin is seeking to sell a majority
stake in state-owned Benin Telecoms SA, Office de Radiodiffusion
et Television du Benin reported, citing Patrick Benon, general
manager of the company.  Benin Telecoms has reduced its debt to 93 billion  CFA
francs  this year from 200 billion francs in 2007, the Cotonou-
based broadcaster said yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Serge-David Zoueme in Porto Novo at 
 zsergedavid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  